ここ ~ koko ~ here (near speaker)
そこ ~ soko ~ there (near listener)
あそこ ~ asoko ~ that over there (far from speaker and listener)
右 ~ migi ~ right
左 ~ hidari ~ left
東 ~ higashi ~ east
西 ~ nishi ~ west
南 ~ minami ~ south 
北 ~ kita ~ north
向かい ~ mukai ~ opposite, other side, across the street
隣 ~ tonari ~ next to, near
前 ~ mae ~ in front of
後ろ ~ ushiro ~ back, behind
まっすぐ ~ massugu ~ straight, direct
道 ~ michi ~ road, street, way, path, route
大学 ~ daigaku ~ university, college
中学校 ~ chuugakkou ~ junior high school, middle school
小学校 ~ shougakkou ~ primary school, elementary school
高校学校 ~ koukougakkou ~ senior high school, high school
病院 ~ byouin ~ hospital
銀行 ~ ginkou ~ bank
駅 ~ eki ~ station
公園 ~ kouen ~ park
動物園　~ doubutsuen ~ zoo
家 ~ ie ~ house
スーパー ~ suupaa ~ super market
川 ~ kawa ~ river
山 ~ yama ~ mountain
海 ~ umi ~ sea
湖 ~ mizuumi ~ lake